org.forgerock.openam.scripting

Class ScriptObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.scripting.ScriptObject

  • public final class ScriptObject
extends Object
    Representation of a script in some scripting language. NB: We use 'ScriptObject' to avoid clashes with the JSR 223 'Script' class.
    Since:
    12.0.0

      • validate

        public List<ScriptError> validate()
        Validate this script for the particular language rules and produces a list of ScriptError instances if any validation errors occurred.
        Returns:
        a list of validation errors if validation failed and an empty list if validation passed.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if script is empty.
